<template lang="html">
      <v-col :cols="4">
        <v-card class="my-2 pa-3">
          RETICULATING SPLINES...
        </v-card>
        <v-card
          class="my-2 pa-3"
          v-for="report in reports"
          :key="report.id"
          :href="report.file">
          Report created on {{report.created_at}}
        </v-card>
      </v-col>
</template>

<script>
import { apiService } from "@/common/api.service.js";

export default {
  name: "ReportList",
  props: {
    scenario: {
      type: Object,
      required: true
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {
      reports: null,
    };
  },
  components: {
  },
  computed: {
    // themeChanged() {
    //   if (this.newTheme === null) {
    //     return false
    //   } else {
    //     return !(this.newTheme === this.scenario.theme)
    //   }
    // }
  },
  methods: {
    getReports() {
      let endpoint = `/api/scenarios/${this.scenario.id}/reports/`;
      apiService(endpoint).then(data => {
        this.reports = data.results;
      });
    },
  },
  mounted() {
    this.getReports()
  },
};
</script>
